              "content": {
                "content": "# \ud83e\udd16 APIM Token Usage Dashboard\n\nMonitor LLM token consumption by caller. Data sourced from `ApiManagementGatewayLlmLog` (actual token counts, even for streaming) joined with `ApiManagementGatewayLogs` (caller identity via x-caller-name header).",
                "title": "APIM Token Usage Dashboard",
                "subtitle": "",
                "markdownSource": 1
              }
            }
